name: Unbeatable Breeze RANDOM INFINITY MODE
description:
Did you hate Unbeatable Breeze? Well, it's not over yet! Try Unbeatable Breeze Random Infinity Mode and jump the buildings forever! It's impossible to get the same level twice! Jump to the end at the right of the level to commence a new one and add to your score! How many levels can you stand?

Left and Right Arrows for movement, Z to jump. Z on the wall of a building to wall hop (Works only once per building!).
